author: killless
title: Great value Alternative!
review:
I have always wanted to get a mini Hulk mini figurine, but the price on the secondary market is way too high to pay for a figurine I feel.

Luckily with the launch of this Hulk keychain figurine, I'm able to own one for a fraction of the price as compared to what I have to pay for the actual figurine.

But of cause there will be others who mind not having the actual figurine. Then this keychain will not be suitable for you.
